  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 3rd level, you gain proficiency in Perception and Martial Arts skills and you can use Strength or Intelligence for checks made with either skill.</p><p>Also, you have developed your own technology to help assist you in your endevors. Hidden throughout your clothes and/or armor are small <strong>Gadgets</strong>. Each gadget is a useful tool that assists you both in combat as well as finding the truth. Select two of the following <em><strong>Gadgets</strong></em>. You can select two more Gadgets at 10th level. You can use these gadgets a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus per long rest.</p>",
